snippet.title: Spellbearers - Nintendo Switch Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Spellbearers is available NOW on Nintendo Switch! Experience magical couch co-op twin-stick shooter action! 

Cast powerful spells, battle against hordes of magical enemies to liberate the rulers of three kingdoms that have been overtaken by dark forces. With staff in hand, do you have what it takes to uphold the title of The Spellbearer?

Purchase today on the Nintendo eShop - https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/pro... 

Trailer by: Jessica M. Jacuinde
#nintendoswitch #spellbearers
